<HEADLINE> 'Gone in 60 Seconds' Tops Box Office  </HEADLINE>
By TOM HARRIGAN
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES (AP) -- The biggest moneymaker at movie theaters so
far this year enjoyed 16 days on top -- then it was ''Gone in 60
Seconds.''
</P>
<P>
